opencom is an open source management system
===========================================

Licensed under the GNU General Public License

Founded by Michael Wulz 2011

You can easily control your home/house with one system. You can add plugins for I/O-communication,XMLRPC connectors for 3rd party programs and much more...

Requires:
- Database (standard MySQL)
- PHP5
- lightHTTPd

This system is designed to run on very-small hardware with low memory consumption.

